This hotel largely meets the standards of other Kimpton Hotels, as indicated in many of the other reviews.	The main reason we chose this hotel was Kimpton has a great reputation and their Seattle hotel was beyond our expectations.	I highly recommend this hotel and the Kimpton brand.	Finally, although the rest of the hotel measures up to the high Kimpton standards (especially the staff), the rooms lack the usual good FM radio/CD/speaker systems that distinguish Kimpton from the pack.	This is a special find if you want to get away from all the generic chain hotels.	We are very impressed with the Kimpton brand.	As with other Kimpton properties the service and amenities were top notch.